text: Ninad Shah (born 7 January 1997) is a Hong Kong cricketer. He made his first- class cricket debut against Ireland in the 2015–17 ICC Intercontinental Cup on 30 August 2016. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Hong Kong cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
